{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"de52bcebb7","title":"中共中央关于地主兼营商业债务纠纷处理办法给中南局的批复","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a39fa96ce","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":15,"articleId":"de52bcebb7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bde7e42973","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于地主兼营商业债务纠纷处理办法给中南局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"},{"id":"c33fa8fcee","type":"appellation","text":"中南局并华南分局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"},{"id":"583dfe4dd1","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月三十日电悉。华南分局关于地主兼营商业的债务纠纷处理办法，中央并未见到。中央同意你们十二月三十日关于这一问题复华南分局电所提的意见。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"},{"id":"ea3d5f37fc","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央一月十五日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"},{"id":"466ab2d9d2","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"},{"id":"24f28d54ef","type":"subtitle","text":"中南局关于地主兼营商业债务纠纷处理办法的请示","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"},{"id":"43d0e0067e","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九五O年十二月三十日）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"},{"id":"5950de1614","type":"appellation","text":"分局报中央：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"},{"id":"9fb86458b9","type":"paragraph","text":"复兴梅关于地主兼营商业债务纠粉[纷]处理办法悉 。同意你们所提的处理原则，但农民向商店赊借糖油等项货物，应视为买卖关系，即便利息过高也不要废除，只有地主通过商店，乘农民困难向其贷款贷粮、谋取高利者，才可当做债务关系，加以废除。其贷货给农民作商业贩卖的资本及买卖欠帐皆系原约处理。以上处理，请中央指示后执行。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"},{"id":"508718b025","type":"paragraph","text":" 中南局十二月三十日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"de52bcebb7"}],"page":{"id":"dc3a69eeda","publicatio